rComments: Extremely unstructured and messy lectures. No slides and no notes, absolutely nothing. Bad at explaining the material and offer little help in office hours.

Worst teacher ever. Strong French accent, gives examples that make absolutely no sense and his assignment question does not reflect the answer he wants. Does not offer you a seat when you go to his office hours (if you're only a lowly undergrad that is). Not helpful, not even a professor but a post doc somehow thought capable of teaching
